TITLE:: NxMessage
summary:: A NexusUI message 
categories:: NexusUI
related:: Classes/NxWidget

DESCRIPTION::
A NexusUI message that outputs message when clicked.


CLASSMETHODS::


INSTANCEMETHODS::

METHOD:: message
The message last sent by the widget this represents.

returns:: A string containing a message.


EXAMPLES::

code::
(
m = NxMessage();
m.message = "button being pressed!";
m.action = { |nx| nx.message.postln };
)

m.message = "a different message";
::
